Final Mental Map

Keep this in your mind:

Basic ML:
Data → Model → Prediction

Real ML:
Data → Cleaning → Feature Engineering → Model → Evaluation

Industry ML:
Data Pipeline → Feature Pipeline → Training Pipeline → Deployment → Monitoring → Retraining

Advanced AI:
ML → Deep Learning → NLP → LLM → RAG → AI Agents

So your learning curve should be:

ML fundamentals
↓
Data preprocessing
↓
Feature engineering
↓
Model training
↓
Model evaluation
↓
Advanced algorithms
↓
Production ML
↓
Deep learning
↓
LLM / GenAI
↓
RAG / AI agents
